{"tid":541492,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"真係睇唔透","createTime":"2018-01-26T13:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T00:25:19.000Z","uid":100519,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bde7c16b54865d43b93662c3ffb1b67753444978","tid":541492,"uid":100519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T13:16:37.000Z","msg":"同個男同事keep ws左大半年，係ws好多野講<br />\n但返工見到對方都扮唔熟咁 <br />\n佢同其他同事野都講一餐 ，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對我就一出聲就串我 好似我講乜都錯咁<br />\n圍內fd既同事會約出去玩，<br />\n但得我同佢住得遠  所以成日一齊搭車<br />\n有幾次通完宵 佢搭的士會兜左我先再返屋企(我同佢住唔近 的士都要80蚊左右，但成日比返錢佢都唔要<br />\n有次飲酒 我同另一女同事都醉醉地<br />\n佢話個女同事自己搞得掂 之後送左我到屋企樓下先走<br />\n<br />\n呢排好似成日係公司避我咁 <br />\n但一放工就回我ws <br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以同我講佢諗緊乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc9eae45964c1f85f822e4ddd1a69480510db471","tid":541492,"uid":119401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T16:31:12.000Z","msg":"呀媽咁笨架"},{"pid":"5b6489cc2bc00172fdb70daef364b1ceea64e7bc","tid":541492,"uid":100519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc9eae45964c1f85f822e4ddd1a69480510db471","tid":541492,"uid":119401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T16:31:12.000Z","msg":"呀媽咁笨架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T23:13:50.000Z","msg":"摸唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877bb79907f99523755f501a03954885d2a153b9","tid":541492,"uid":33004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T23:16:37.000Z","msg":"做d野咁似d小朋友中意人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"352f18781464e9c4837222d1153dac64d59d118f","tid":541492,"uid":71349,"like":0,"dislike":0,